It could be both definition 20(11) and definition 27 (9).

It could be 20(11) as it talks about the rumours as being non-corporal things that surrounded Moriarty's reputation at the University, due the rumours coming from everyone and all directions.

It could also be 27 (9), as that paints the rumours as attacks in speech and writing which ultimately made Moriarty resign from the University, after attacking his reputation.;

It could be definition 01(50) and definition 07 (36) as well.

It could be 01(50) as Sherlock may be referring to the mysterious power getting the way of the law (rules) of the society from being upheld in a more metaphorical sense.

It could also be 07(36) as Sherlock may be referring to the mysterious power as literally getting the way of the law enforcers (like the policemen) from doing their job and arresting those responsible.;

